WEBVTT

00:03:57.954 --> 00:04:02.496
bo’lishni yoqtiraman. Men Meksikaga bordim
va suv ostidadelfinlar bilan suzdim.

00:04:03.246 --> 00:04:05.621
Va o’sha yili men qilgan yana bir 
ajoyib narsa

00:04:05.663 --> 00:04:07.746
menga tog’ bo’lgan

00:04:07.746 --> 00:04:09.663
“Men sizga hukm chiqarayapman:

00:04:09.663 --> 00:04:11.746
yaxshiroq bajarish bo’yicha qo’llanma”

00:04:11.746 --> 00:04:12.913
kitobini yozdim.

00:04:12.913 --> 00:04:13.954
Va men --
(Qarsaklar)

00:04:13.954 --> 00:04:15.788
endi esa yozish masalasi, to’g’rimi?

00:04:15.788 --> 00:04:17.038
Ha.

00:04:17.038 --> 00:04:20.079
Lekin meni eng qo’rqitgan va 
menga hos bo’lmagan

00:04:20.121 --> 00:04:21.913
narsani qildim va bu -- 
Men

00:04:22.913 --> 00:04:24.413
parashyutdan sakrashga bordim.

00:04:25.538 --> 00:04:27.329
Biz samolyotdan sakrash arafasidamiz.

00:04:27.371 --> 00:04:30.829
O’zimga, “Men hayotda ahmoqona
narsalar qilganman, bu ulardan biri.”